window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Book 2 of Wild Era.</b></p> <p>The Lord of Wildfire has been reborn, but the Wild Era is full of dangers and his strength needs to rise.</p> <p>He has disrupted the plans of Baron Verasun and the Sarathian Empire, creating enemies both near and far, while the enemies who killed him in his first life are still out there.</p> <p>His rise is meteoric, but the Path of Stars is ignoring him, so he has to forge his own path to power.</p> <p>With the Stars Alliance and his old knowledge on his side, he sets his sight on the things that can help him the most: the Chaos Remnants.</p> <p>These mystical dungeons cover the world, full of experience, artifacts, and other rewards that can shape his life and grant him steady progress. Only by conquering them will his Evolutions be smooth.</p> <p>His immediate goals mix with the need to look after his two young apprentices, Yao and Naomi, and help them plan for their own classes.</p> <p>Fortunately, he's good at all of it.</p>"; 
